  "title": "Facility Officer| Building Maintenance & Management",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Facility &amp; Building Maintenance Support Executive</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Industry: Singapore Preschool Settings</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>5 days (Mon – Fri) 9am - 6pm</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic Salary : $3,000 - $4,500 + Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Headquarter near Labrador Park MRT, Singapore</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements: [ Must fulfill all 2 ]</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in facility management, property management or related fields</li>\n  <li>Diploma or Certificate in Building &amp; Facilities Management or relevant</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the coordination of all maintenance, repair and renovation projects</li>\n  <li>Respond to request for maintenance work</li>\n  <li>Investigate, check and analyse reported breakdowns and faults to determine their causes for the prevention of future occurrence</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of all work performed and ensure timely completion of all work request records</li>\n  <li>Keep proper records of legal contracts and vendor information and monitor the expiry of contracts</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with vendors and contractors to ensure that all work is completed in a timely and satisfactory manner. This includes working with the contractors to schedule pest control and air-conditioning</li>\n  <li>Providing support in building and development projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p>\n<p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p>\n<p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
